name: The Great Tengu
description:
Heroes of the Far East #2

A Demon inhabit a particular mountain in the Far East region.
Taking the appearance of semi-human mixed with avian characteristic, with a bright red color.

Those who wander too deep inside the mountain forest are abducted, later to be tormented but other times they are teaching them magic.

The Great Tengu are master at swordsmanship, capable of controlling strong wind and taking flight. A proud being with penchant for chaos and savagery.

They are said to cause wars and bring natural disasters. 
Truly one of the most powerful being in the Far East.
